<P>
President Corazon Aquino today signed a service contract with Royal Dutch Shell 
and Los Angeles-based Occidental Petroleum Corp. for the exploration and 
development of potentially rich natural gas deposits in the Camago area off 
northern Palawan Island. 
</P>
