<TEXT>
<P>
The pub where Rob Moroso drank beer before his fatal accident Sept. 30 is not 
to blame for the wreck that killed the rookie NASCAR driver and another person, 
the state Alcohol Law Enforcement division said today. 
</P>
<P>
